&lt;thead&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;th&gt;Pros&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;th&gt;Cons&lt;/th&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/thead&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Increases efficiency and productivity&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Potential job displacement&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Reduces human error&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Initial implementation costs can be high&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Provides valuable insights for decision-making&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Requires ongoing maintenance and updates&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Enhances employee satisfaction by reducing mundane tasks&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;td&gt;Data privacy and security concerns&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
